ips    UIC Connection    Contact Us    UIC menu    UIC.edu    Campus Map       Search                        Student Life     View Menu  Down arrow icon             With one of the most diverse student populations in the nation, the University of Illinois at Chicago is dedicated to providing a welcoming environment for its students and fostering a sense of belonging, academic success, student growth and development, diversity, and community.      Student Life        Campus Housing  Promoting a vibrant living environment in the heart of Chicago          Student Leadership and Civic Engagement  Providing student-centered co-curricular leadership and service programming.          Center for Student Involvement  Holistic development through educational, social, leadership, and cultural programming for UIC students          Commuter Student Resource Center  Educating our campus on understanding the commuter student experience.          Campus Dining & Meal Plans  Meeting the nutritional needs and the environmental expectations of University students, faculty, staff and visitors.          Fraternity & Sorority Life  Providing oversight and guidance to 30+ fraternities and sororities at UIC          Student Life        Student Centers  Creating opportunities for memorable experiences through innovative programs, services, and facilities.          Student Organizations  Holistic development through educational, social, leadership, and cultural programming for UIC students.          UIC Impact  Students apply their learning to real world challenges through high impact engagement.          Credit Union 1 Arena  Bringing students and faculty together for exciting sports, concerts, gatherings and events.          U & I Care  Strengthening the UIC network of care for students.          UIC Connection, UIC Life           UIC Connection  UIC Connection is your way to get involved!             UIC Life  Connect with us on Social Media              Student Life    Back to main conte